sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant Browser as Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuthProxy as oauth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP TLS
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Istio as Istio Gateway<br/>8445/TCP TLS
    participant Authorino as Authorino<br/>AuthConfig
    participant KServeCtrl as KServe Controller
    participant Predictor as Inference Runtime<br/>(vLLM/OVMS/TGIS)<br/>8012/TCP mTLS
    participant S3 as S3/Object Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DSP as DSP API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow<br/>Controller
    participant MLMD as ML Metadata<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant MariaDB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP
    participant GuardGW as Orchestrator Gateway<br/>8090/TCP HTTP
    participant GuardOrch as Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8033/TCP HTTP
    participant Detectors as Guardrails Detectors<br/>8000/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Detectors: Flow 1: Dashboard Access

    User->>Browser: Access RHOAI Dashboard
    Browser->>Router: HTTPS/443 (TLS 1.2+)
    Router->>OAuthProxy: Reencrypt TLS
    OAuthProxy->>OAuthProxy: OpenShift OAuth validation
    OAuthProxy->>Dashboard: HTTP/8080 (x-forwarded-access-token)
    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/6443 (user Bearer Token)
    K8sAPI-->>Dashboard: API Response
    Dashboard-->>Browser: HTML/JSON Response

    Note over User,Detectors: Flow 2: KServe Serverless Inference

    User->>Router: POST /v1/models/{model}:predict<br/>HTTPS/443
    Router->>Istio: TLS Passthrough
    Istio->>Authorino: AuthConfig validation
    Authorino-->>Istio: Auth OK
    Istio->>Predictor: HTTP/8012 (mTLS via Istio)
    Predictor->>S3: Load model weights<br/>HTTPS/443
    S3-->>Predictor: Model artifacts
    Predictor-->>Istio: Inference result
    Istio-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>User: JSON prediction

    Note over User,Detectors: Flow 3: Pipeline Execution

    User->>DSP: Create Pipeline Run<br/>HTTP/8888
    DSP->>Argo: Create Workflow CR
    Argo->>K8sAPI: Create executor Pods
    K8sAPI-->>Argo: Pods created
    loop Each pipeline step
        Argo->>Argo: Execute step in Pod
        Argo->>S3: Store artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443
        Argo->>MLMD: Record metadata<br/>gRPC/8080
        Argo->>MariaDB: Persist status<br/>MySQL/3306
    end
    Argo-->>DSP: Workflow complete
    DSP-->>User: Run status

    Note over User,Detectors: Flow 4: Guardrailed LLM Request

    User->>GuardGW: POST /{route}/v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/8090
    GuardGW->>GuardOrch: Forward + inject detector config<br/>HTTP/8033
    par Input Detection
        GuardOrch->>Detectors: PII/toxicity check<br/>HTTP/8000
        Detectors-->>GuardOrch: Detection results
    end
    alt Input flagged
        GuardOrch-->>GuardGW: Fallback message
    else Input clean
        GuardOrch->>Predictor: Generate (vLLM InferenceService)
        Predictor-->>GuardOrch: Generated text
        par Output Detection
            GuardOrch->>Detectors: Output safety check<br/>HTTP/8000
            Detectors-->>GuardOrch: Detection results
        end
        alt Output flagged
            GuardOrch-->>GuardGW: Fallback message
        else Output clean
            GuardOrch-->>GuardGW: Generated response
        end
    end
    GuardGW-->>User: Final response
